        "title": "Our Story",
        "story": "## From Farm to Table\n\nFounded in 2014, The Restaurant began as a small neighborhood bistro with a simple mission: serve honest food made from the finest local ingredients.\n\nOver the years, we have grown into one of the city's most beloved dining destinations, but our philosophy remains the same. We partner directly with local farmers, fishermen, and artisan producers to bring you dishes that are as fresh as they are flavorful.\n\n## Our Philosophy\n\nWe believe great food starts with great ingredients. Our menu changes with the seasons, reflecting what is at its peak. Our kitchen team draws inspiration from culinary traditions around the world, blending classic techniques with modern creativity.\n\nWhether you are joining us for a casual weeknight dinner or a special celebration, we want every visit to feel like coming home.",
